Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.16,0:00:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.36,0:00:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Meimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.07,0:00:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.27,0:00:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning. It's getting\Nso cold these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.61,0:00:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course it is.\NChristmas is almost here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.48,0:00:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Christmas. Wouldn't it be nice\Nif it snowed?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.93,0:00:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It certainly would.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.03,0:00:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Has anybody noticed how quiet\Nthe class has gotten lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.95,0:00:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And the reason is\Nright over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.39,0:00:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Asuka Jr.?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.79,0:00:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,He hasn't received any notes\Nfrom St. Tail lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.77,0:00:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's why\Nhe's been down in the dumps.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.87,0:00:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand how he feels.\NHe misses the chase.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.38,0:00:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that why he's so gloomy? How silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.33,0:00:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheer up, Asuka Jr.!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.30,0:00:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. It's only you, Haneoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.55,0:00:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,How rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.12,0:01:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So what if St. Tail doesn't appear?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.19,0:01:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It only proves\Nthe world is at peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.79,0:01:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.90,0:01:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you jabber so much\Nfirst thing in the morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.87,0:01:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I can't stand\Nthe girls in this class.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.34,0:01:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.75,0:01:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You're all nosy, loud-mouthed\Nand unfeminine on top of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.43,0:01:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, then tell me\Nwhat's your ideal girl like, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.07,0:01:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.64,0:01:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not you, that's for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.11,0:01:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no such thing\Nas the perfect girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.36,0:01:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, there is!\NTake St. Tail, for example.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.54,0:01:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with you?\NIt's always St. Tail, St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.82,0:01:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.13,0:01:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Meimi?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.00,0:01:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You moron!\NI hate you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.22,0:01:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm St. Tail.\NAnd if I'm her, then why...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.68,0:02:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Surprise!\NThe Large Lizard Santa Claus?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.96,0:02:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayu, isn't it?\NThere's no one here but me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.97,0:02:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You can tell me\Nyour problem now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.17,0:02:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister, Goh stole Tama from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.82,0:02:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Goh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.99,0:02:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,He's in my class\Nand he's so mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.83,0:02:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not even bothering him...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.64,0:02:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,but he kicks my blocks\Nand hits me with the ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.41,0:02:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And he's the one\Nwho stole your pet, Tama?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.55,0:02:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.42,0:02:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you tell your mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.60,0:02:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But Mama hates animals.\NShe said he should keep Tama.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.44,0:02:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.88,0:03:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I really love Tama.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.66,0:03:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand. Don't cry.\NI'm sure God will help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.43,0:03:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.51,0:03:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.18,0:03:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Goh is really Gohta Ogasawara.\NHe's five years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.19,0:03:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And he lives on the hill\Non the outskirts of town.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.90,0:03:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And what does Tama look like?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.34,0:03:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,She's black in color and\Nhas a ribbon around her neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.02,0:03:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I think she'll be easy to spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.36,0:03:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright. I guess I'll go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.40,0:03:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, what about a\Nnote to Asuka Jr.?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.67,0:03:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget it.\NWho cares about that promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.71,0:03:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That means\Nyou'll be breaking the promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.39,0:03:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.03,0:03:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Meimi...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.20,0:03:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,He only thinks of St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.98,0:03:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sending another\Nnote to that guy. Not ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.10,0:04:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The bully's room\Nshould be underneath me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.35,0:04:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.33,0:04:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're the little meany.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.00,0:04:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd better start\Nthinking about how girls feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.21,0:04:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Or you'll end up like\Na certain blockhead I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.86,0:04:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Phew. Gee, I almost forgot.\NNow, where's that Tama?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.35,0:04:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Here Tama... Oh, Tama...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.10,0:05:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Black in color,\Nwith a ribbon. It can't be, can it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.18,0:05:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,TAMA\NAre you Tama? I thought you'd\Nbe a cute little black cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.94,0:05:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What'll I do?\NI'm too scared to touch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.52,0:05:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means I can't steal it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.39,0:05:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,This is ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.79,0:05:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,My reputation is at stake.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.31,0:05:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Tama, what's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.14,0:06:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.51,0:06:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll call it quits for tonight.\NI've got to get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.50,0:06:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Detective Asuka, over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.37,0:06:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,After her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.51,0:06:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's St. Tail! After her!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.09,0:06:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.95,0:06:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got her cornered now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.26,0:06:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.81,0:06:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I warned you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.33,0:06:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.54,0:06:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Detective Asuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.14,0:06:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't hang on to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.14,0:06:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't help it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.48,0:07:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.31,0:07:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,-Don't do that, sir!\N-Help, I'm sinking!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.90,0:07:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,St. Tail appears!\NBut what is her target?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.87,0:07:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The mystery thickens!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.21,0:07:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Detective Asuka\Nmisses the arrest by an inch!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.49,0:07:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been pretty long\Nsince St. Tail's last caper.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.39,0:07:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard your Dad came close\Nto capturing her this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.44,0:07:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, Asuka?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.11,0:07:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!\NShe never sent me a note!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.95,0:07:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.75,0:07:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Who does she think\Nshe's dealing with, anyway?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.99,0:07:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down, Asuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.30,0:07:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I was waiting for a note!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.01,0:07:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Why'd she do it\Nwithout letting me know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.08,0:07:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What'll I do?\NIt's all my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.99,0:07:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheer up. I'm sure she just\Nforgot her promise to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.53,0:07:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not like that!\NShe'd never break her promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.11,0:07:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'm sure she has\Na very good reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.35,0:07:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Just mind your own business!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.05,0:07:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to hear your ideas\Nabout St. Tail's motives!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.36,0:08:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! You'll never capture St. Tail,\Nnot in a million years!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.08,0:08:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, be quiet!\NYou don't know anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.88,0:08:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.85,0:08:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.96,0:08:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I do!\NBecause I'm St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.87,0:08:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Meimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.77,0:08:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?\NWhat was that about St. Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.38,0:08:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.71,0:08:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, brother,\NI can't believe I said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.93,0:08:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Ruby, do you think\NAsuka caught what I said?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.41,0:08:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,SEIKA NEWS STATION
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.82,0:08:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Good evening.\NThis is the Seika News Station.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.73,0:08:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Our first story this evening features\Nthe city's Christmas Eve festivities...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.18,0:09:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you!\NHow'd you get in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.18,0:09:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't be here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.52,0:09:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama, come look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.03,0:09:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, Papa?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.80,0:09:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that Meimi's classmate on TV?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.45,0:09:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.25,0:09:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a break!\NI'll make it quick!\NSee? It's that smart kid.\NThe mayor's pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.19,0:09:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not possible right now!\NYou're right.\NI wonder what he's doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.10,0:09:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Meimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.63,0:09:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Grump!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.84,0:09:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow! Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.91,0:09:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Hey! That's my mic!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.21,0:09:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, Mama?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.21,0:09:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.65,0:09:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a message for St. Tail!\NMeet me tonight at Park A!\NLook, isn't that boy in your class?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.66,0:09:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a message for St. Tail!\NMeet me tonight at Park A!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.23,0:09:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be waiting alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.21,0:09:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm doomed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.28,0:09:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't come,\NI'll reveal your identity...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.08,0:09:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,...to the entire city!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.69,0:09:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no escaping those eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.74,0:09:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Quick! Cut the cameras! Cut!\NYou hear me?!\NI'll repeat it once more!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.24,0:09:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Please Stand By\NSEIKA TV
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.18,0:09:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,St. Tail, eh?\NI'll bet she's a beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.29,0:10:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like when you were younger.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.36,0:10:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I'm still beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.04,0:10:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Meimi, what do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.81,0:10:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Meimi? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.42,0:10:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You mustn't go. It's a bluff.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.36,0:10:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It might be one\Nof Asuka Jr's. tricks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.04,0:10:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.\NDo you think I'm crazy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.29,0:10:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'm going to be caught,\NI have this funny feeling...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.67,0:10:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,it'd be better if Asuka\Nwas the one to catch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.57,0:10:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Meimi...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.24,0:10:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think\NI shouldn't go, Seira?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.96,0:10:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It wouldn't do any good\Nto stop you, would it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.27,0:10:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But listen, Meimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.31,0:11:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You must never reveal your\Nidentity to him on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.68,0:11:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You must take him by surprise\Nas you've always done.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.12,0:11:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.02,0:11:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't know how much\Nhe really knows, do we?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.67,0:11:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, you have\Na job to do tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.95,0:11:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.82,0:11:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, for Mayu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.86,0:11:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right.\NI haven't gotten Tama back yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.60,0:11:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Poor Mayu. She's been waiting\Nanxiously for Tama.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.68,0:11:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right. But why\Ndoes it have to be tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.89,0:11:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth is,\NMayu and her family are moving...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.36,0:11:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,to another city far from here\Ntomorrow, Christmas Day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.67,0:11:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,She's moving away?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.25,0:11:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayu, just forget about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.53,0:11:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why tonight\Nis the last chance you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.15,0:11:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, Seira.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.92,0:11:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's give her an\Nunforgettable Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.46,0:12:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.97,0:12:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Meimi, when the time comes that\Nyou're captured, we'll go together.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.10,0:12:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord, forgive me\Nfor I use no gimmick or trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.69,0:12:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,One!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.43,0:12:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.47,0:12:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.88,0:12:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,May the blessings\Nof God be with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.48,0:13:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe she wasn't watching TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.24,0:13:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Snow... It's going to be a white\NChristmas. Brr... it's freezing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.94,0:13:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess\Nshe's not going to show.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.46,0:13:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?\NSt. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.81,0:13:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You must take him by surprise,\Nas you've always done.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.26,0:14:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what good it'll do but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.11,0:14:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Show Time!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.66,0:14:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.97,0:14:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you stop?\NI've had enough of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.59,0:14:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you think\NI left that cell phone over there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.80,0:14:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen! I'm not leaving here,\Nso you can just relax!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.11,0:14:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.48,0:14:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! But you said\Nyou'd reveal my identity...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.09,0:14:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a bluff!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.23,0:14:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, brother.\NHe doesn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.97,0:14:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind that.\NWhy didn't you send me a note?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.21,0:14:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,How do I explain?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.78,0:14:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that why you called me here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.19,0:14:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,This is very important,\Nso listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.13,0:14:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what it means...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.44,0:14:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,if you don't let me know\Nwhere you're going to strike.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.61,0:15:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It means I won't be there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.55,0:15:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And that means... um... er...\Nlet's put it this way...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.90,0:15:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What'll happen if\Nsomebody else captures you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.94,0:15:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.54,0:15:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... what I'm saying!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.35,0:15:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.59,0:15:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm coming over.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.99,0:15:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.24,0:15:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me, Seira.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.01,0:15:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You must never reveal\Nyour identity to him on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.59,0:15:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.90,0:15:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn, the glass is\Nso fogged up, I can't see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.62,0:15:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.61,0:15:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.25,0:15:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.16,0:16:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,My promise...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.13,0:16:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I broke my promise.\NI'll never do it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.91,0:16:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.39,0:16:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.93,0:16:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.00,0:16:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.17,0:16:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want you to\Ngive up on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.75,0:16:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.99,0:16:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,St. Tail! Don't get caught\Nuntil I catch up with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.84,0:16:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.07,0:16:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a promise!\NDon't you forget!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.22,0:16:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.00,0:16:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,"I am going to\Nthe Ogasawara residence..."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.04,0:17:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,"this evening to take\Ntheir pet, Tama - St. Tail."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.02,0:17:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Tonight?!\NI don't have much time left!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.83,0:17:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn her!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.40,0:17:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry,\Nbut tonight's the only night.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.98,0:17:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Tama's not here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.99,0:17:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,"Don't be mean to little girls!"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.31,0:17:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.82,0:17:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?!\NSt. Tail has shown up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.33,0:17:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Daddy, Mommy, wake up -\Nyou gotta see this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.07,0:17:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Santa is flying in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.18,0:17:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Santa is flying in the sky?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.38,0:17:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be dreaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.42,0:17:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.77,0:17:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Santa Claus?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.64,0:17:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Santa!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.43,0:18:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! Presents from Santa!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.60,0:18:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Police vehicle coming through!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.74,0:18:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Clear the street!\NI repeat, clear the street!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.55,0:18:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn... she got away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.30,0:18:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayu, forget about Tama and go to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.99,0:18:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Tama! Tama's come home!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.30,0:18:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Tama, oh Tama!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.72,0:18:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess we have no choice but\Nto take Tama with us, right, Mayu?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.32,0:18:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurray!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.13,0:18:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurray!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.52,0:19:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,St. Tail...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.82,0:19:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get you\Nfor sure next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.23,0:19:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Merry Christmas!
